Quarantine Breaches Data

breaches_data.Rd

Contains individual quarantine breach events in Australia.

Usage

breaches_data

Format

A tibble with 39 rows and 9 columns:

no

Record number

state

State or territory code

date

Date of the breach event

facility

Facility name

case_name

Role or person involved

variant

COVID-19 variant, if known

onward

Whether community transmission occurred (TRUE/FALSE)

vax

Vaccination status if available

link

Reference URL for the report
